lead_paragraph: Venezuela have named their former goalkeeper Rafael Dudamel as coach after a string of defeats in the 2018 World Cup qualifying campaign amid severe financial problems, the country's soccer federation (FVF) said on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Cash-Strapped Strugglers Venezuela Appoint Dudamel as Coach
